sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Sched as Scheduler/Manual Trigger
  participant AISvc as AIService
  participant Agg as AggregationService
  participant AggDB as aggregateData
  participant IAApi as Python IA API
  participant ForecastDB as lstmForecast
  participant AnomDB as anomalyDetection
  participant API as /api/ia/*
  participant UI as Frontend IA panel

  Sched->>AISvc: runForecastForZone(zoneId)
  AISvc->>Agg: syncHourlyAggregatesForZone(lookback 48h)
  Agg->>AggDB: upsert HOURLY aggregates
  AISvc->>AggDB: buildLookbackMatrix(zoneId)
  AISvc->>IAApi: POST /forecast (LSTM input matrix)
  IAApi-->>AISvc: forecast horizons + confidence
  AISvc->>ForecastDB: save latest forecast

  Sched->>AISvc: runAnomalyDetectionForZone(zoneId)
  AISvc->>IAApi: POST /anomaly-detect
  IAApi-->>AISvc: anomaly score + label
  AISvc->>AnomDB: save detection

  UI->>API: GET /api/ia/forecast/latest/:zoneId
  API->>ForecastDB: find latest by zone
  API-->>UI: forecast data

  UI->>API: GET /api/ia/anomalies/:zoneId
  API->>AnomDB: history(limit)
  API-->>UI: anomalies history